{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":25669,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":4311,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"改革是必要的. 然而他的改革没有动摇斯大林体制, 实际上是以对赫鲁晓夫的个人崇拜取代对斯大林的个人崇拜. ","timestamp":1592911090,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":25673,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":4311,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 那个时候还是文艺解冻，经济宽松的吧","timestamp":1592911143,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":25712,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":4311,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 只是做了一点小的放松, 文艺其实也没解冻得很多, 害怕被解冻的洪流冲垮. 经济条条管理变成块块管理, 还是统得很死, 没有根本改变斯大林留下来的体制. 勃列日涅夫一上来刷刷刷全搞回去了.","timestamp":1592911516,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":25725,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":4311,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"感觉比勋章帝还是好一些的","timestamp":1592911600,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":25932,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":4311,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"赫鲁晓夫的问题在于三和两全，党失去了先进性，成为了奴役国民欺压国外的老大哥实体。由此，整个国家开始实际上走资本主义道路。","timestamp":1592912936,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":25972,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":4311,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 有点赞同","timestamp":1592913160,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{"h":1080,"w":1080},"likenum":3,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":4311,"reply":6,"tag":null,"text":"请问大家如何看待赫鲁晓瓶啊，写毛概论文时候看历史上对他评价两极分化","timestamp":1592910986,"type":"image","updated_at":1606782584,"url":"bo/bozasv5fohgwqytwsvfduw7zykqnztsy.jpeg","vote":{}}}